						<p>"I want to know the future" "You can not" "But what about just this one thing ?" "No." "Well, sometimes I can do things, such as pull on my weewee." "Wait... wut ?!" "If there is a way to know the future let me know".</p>
<p>What the everloving fuck nonsense is this. You may not protect specific and specified idiocy through pretending to replace it with other things.</p>
